title: Isinbayeva targets Portland world indoors for comeback
text: Isinbayeva targets Portland world indoors for comeback Tuesday, 20 October 2015 (5 minutes ago) MOSCOW (AP) " Yelena Isinbayeva, the world record-holder and two-time Olympic champion in the pole vault, is targeting next year's world indoor championships in Portland, Oregon, for her return to top-level competition ahead of the...
